Color
: Carapace dark reddish brown, with the margin darker, chelicerae, and posterior part of the cephalic region darker. Abdomen brown, dorsally lighter, booklungs with light markings. Sternum light reddish brown, with labium and maxillae darker. Legs like carapace with light tarsi-metatarsi. Spinnerets light yellow
.
